<body>
<h1><strong>width(value)</strong></h1>
<h2>概述</h2>
<p>canvas方法之一。 为canvas对象设置宽度</p>
<h3>参数:value</h3>
<p>宽度的数值</p>
<h3>描述:</h3>
<p>为canvas对象设置宽度</p>

<h4>HTML 代码:</h4>
<pre>&lt;canvas id="test" width="507px" height="320px" style="border:1px solid #F00"&gt;</pre>
<h4>elves 代码:</h4>
<pre>
$(function() {   
	$("#test").canvas("desk")    <span class="green">//初始化canvas</span>
    $("$desk").width(800);  <span class="green">//选中刚刚初始化的canvas对象，将宽度设置为800</span>
});
</pre>
<h4>demo:</h4>
<p>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../src/elves.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../../src/plugin/dom.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
function setWidth(){
	var widthValue = document.getElementById("widthValue").value;  
	$("#test").canvas("desk")     
    $("$desk").width(widthValue);
}
</script>
<canvas id="test" width="507px" height="320px" style="border:1px solid #F00"></canvas>
<br />
填写canvas的新宽度<input id="widthValue" type="text" value="300" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<input type="button" onClick="setWidth()" value="修改宽度">
</p>
</body>
</html>
